cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically person re-identification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep learning-based method, which suggests that it could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of LSTM-based RNN, which could place it under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves the transfer of knowledge, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on a benchmark dataset, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
